room_title: Escape room "The Medieval Breakout" by Conundrum Escape Rooms in Durango
room_description: King Alfred the great has just discovered that his prized family crests have gone missing. Convinced it was one of the many notorious thieves in the village, the king has ordered a round up of all. The thieves (players) find themselves locked into the castles dungeon and given a ultimatum. Either prove your innocent and restore the crests, or be executed with in the hour. You know you are innocent, but can you figure out how to prove it and regain the favor of the King?
